Class AccuracyUpdatedEnsemble1

  • java.lang.Object

            • moa.classifiers.meta.AccuracyUpdatedEnsemble1
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, Classifier, AWTRenderable, MOAObject, OptionHandler

    public class AccuracyUpdatedEnsemble1
extends AccuracyWeightedEnsemble
    The Accuracy Updated Ensemble classifier as proposed by Brzezinski and Stefanowski in "Accuracy Updated Ensemble for Data Streams with Concept Drift", HAIS 2011. A newer/revised version of this algorithm exists and is called AccuracyUpdatedEnsemble2.
